
Text2Cypher Tool 
Name: Tool for system-wide aggregation questions

Description: **Purpose:**
Answer repo-graph questions and generate **Cypher queries with visual graph results** (nodes + relationships) for Neo4j.

**Schema:**
**Nodes:** Repository, Directory, File, Class, Function, Method, Variable, Parameter, Module, Decorator.
**Rels:** CONTAINS, DEFINES, CALLS, IMPORTS, HAS_PARAMETER.


Similarity Search Tools

Name: Find Similar Functions

Description: Search for functions similar to a query



Find Similar Files

Description: Search for files  similar to a query



Find Similar Classes

Description: Search for classes similar to a query
